&lt;li&gt;Update Latvian translations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=Edgars+Weblate@gaitenis.id.lv"&gt;Edgars Andersons&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Latvian translations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=coool@mail.lv"&gt;‚ÑÇùï†ùï†ùï†ùïù (ùïòùïöùï•ùïôùï¶ùïì.ùïîùï†ùïû/‚ÑÇùï†ùï†ùï†ùïù)&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Polish translations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=dakilla@gmail.com"&gt;≈Åukasz Horodecki&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Slovak translations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=russssty@users.noreply.hosted.weblate.org"&gt;Russssty&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Spanish translations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=jumase@disroot.org"&gt;Juan M Sevilla&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
