  <entry>
    <id>https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/releases/tag/v2.15.0</id>
    <title>New release for Pachli: Pachli 2.15.0</title>
    <updated>2025-07-30T06:10:48-04:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>pachli/pachli-android</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;h3&gt;New features and other improvements&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Show role badges in timelines and account lists (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1687"&gt;1687&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Show moderation warning notifications (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1672"&gt;1672&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pause video playback when swiping through media (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1653"&gt;1653&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement edge-to-edge support (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1650"&gt;1650&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use the new emoji picker for emoji reactions on announcements (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1634"&gt;1634&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Allow user to toggle video/audio playback "repeat" mode (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Allow user to display video subtitles, if present (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pause video/audio player if headphones are disabled (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add button to mute/unmute video/audio playback, with default preference (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Show emojis grouped by category, and searchable (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1624"&gt;1624&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
