&lt;li&gt;Show the account's username (includes domain) when replying (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1688"&gt;1688&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply edge-to-edge margin insets to the "Add tab" popup sheet (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1685"&gt;1685&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reduce network calls when filtering notifications (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1684"&gt;1684&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prevent NPE where TimelineViewModel.repository might be null (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1671"&gt;1671&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Don't crash with network activity on the main thread sharing media (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1660"&gt;1660&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prevent empty lists when tapping on tabs (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1656"&gt;1656&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prevent visual "stutter" when first showing playback controls (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1647"&gt;1647&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Show additional space between video playback controls and progress bar (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1648"&gt;1648&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Don't crash when managing accounts on older API devices (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1646"&gt;1646&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use correct icon color/spacing for the add media buttons when composing (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1645"&gt;1645&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Don't crash if emoji drawable is null (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1631"&gt;1631&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Don't crash when showing dialog to choose a push provider (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1630"&gt;1630&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Correctly display emoji with landscape dimensions (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1626"&gt;1626&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Show an account's emoji's when replying (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1629"&gt;1629&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Show emojis in descriptions of "obscured" links (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1620"&gt;1620&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
